#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72 index.docbook:1661
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Introduction to &konsole;"
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "សេចក្ដី​ណែនាំ​អំពី​កុងសូល"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is a terminal?"
msgstr "តើ​ស្ថានីយ​ជាអ្វី​ ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsole; is an X terminal emulator, often referred to as a terminal or a "
"shell. It emulates a command line interface in a text only window."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsole; typically runs a command shell, an application that executes "
"commands that you type. The shell the &konsole; runs depends on your account "
"settings. Consult your operating system documentation to know what the shell "
"is, how to configure it and how to use it."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:88
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "--noscrollbar"
msgid "Scrollback"
msgstr "--noscrollbar"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&konsole; uses the notion of scrollback to allow users to view previously "
"displayed output. By default, scrollback is on and set to save 1000 lines of "
"output in addition to what is currently displayed on the screen."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As lines scroll off the top of the screen, they can be reviewed by moving "
#| "the scroll bar upwards, scrolling with a mouse wheel or through the use "
#| "of the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Page Up</keycap></"
#| "keycombo> (to move back a page), <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;"
#| "<keycap>Page Down</keycap></keycombo> (to move forward a page), <keycombo "
#| "action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Up Arrow</keycap></keycombo> (to move up "
#| "a line) and <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Down Arrow</"
#| "keycap></keycombo> (to move down a line) keys (provided the <link linkend="
#| "\"settings-menu\">History</link> option is on)."
msgid ""
"As lines of text scroll off the top of the screen, they can be reviewed by "
"moving the scroll bar upwards, scrolling with a mouse wheel or through the "
"use of the <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Page Up</keycap></"
"keycombo> (to move back), <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Page "
"Down</keycap></keycombo> (to move forward), <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Shift;<keycap>Up Arrow</keycap></keycombo> (to move up a line) and "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keycap>Down Arrow</keycap></keycombo> (to "
"move down a line) keys."
msgstr ""
"ព្រោះថា ការ​រមូរ​បន្ទាត់​បានបិទ​នៅ​លើ​កំពូល​របស់​អេក្រង់ ពួក​វា​អាច​ត្រូវ​បាន​ពិនិត្យ​ឡើង​វិញ​ដោយ​ផ្លាស់ទី​"
"របាររមូរទៅ​លើ រមូរ​ដោយ​ប្រើ​កង់កណ្ដុរ ឬ​តាមរយៈ​ប្រើ​គ្រាប់ចុច <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>ប្ដូរ​(Shift)+ទំព័រលើ</keycap></keycombo> (ដើម្បី​ផ្លាស់ទី​ទំព័រ​ថយក្រោយ) "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>​ប្ដូរ​(Shift)+ទំព័រក្រោម</keycap></keycombo> "
"(ដើម្បី​ផ្លាស់ទី​ទំព័រ​ទៅ​មុខ) <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>ប្ដូរ​(Shift)+ព្រួញ​ឡើង​លើ</"
"keycap></keycombo> (ដើម្បី​ផ្លាស់ទី​បន្ទាត់​ឡើង​លើ) ហើយ <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>ប្ដូរ​(Shift)+ព្រួញ​ចុះក្រោម</keycap></keycombo> (ដើម្បី​ផ្លាស់ទី​បន្ទាត់​ចុះក្រោម)"
"(ជម្រើស​ <link linkend=\"settings-menu\">ប្រវត្តិ</link> ដែល​បាន​ផ្ដល់​​បាន​បើក) ។"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can also open a new session with a key shortcut. By default, "
#| "<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> is "
