#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A shell program running in Konsole may emit escape sequences that partition "
"the text displayed into three types: shell prompt, user input and command "
"output. Using this semantic information enables various enhancements in "
"Konsole."
msgstr ""

